[SN]TITLE[SN]
How Indians are celebrating Christmas

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Millions of Indians are celebrating Christmas throughout the country.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
With 24 million followers, Christianity is India's third-largest religion. Christians comprise 2.3% of the country's population.
